FBIS4-67191 "jptdd021__l94044" JPRS-TDD-94-021-L JPRS Narcotics 14 May 1994 EAST ASIA LAOS Over 2,000 Kg of Marijuana Destroyed in Vientiane Over 2,000 Kg of Marijuana Destroyed in Vientiane BK1405090194 Vientiane Vitthayou Hengsat Radio Network in Lao 0000 GMT 14 May 94 BK1405090194 Vientiane Vitthayou Hengsat Radio Network Lao BFN [Text] Some 2,380 kilos of dry and raw marijuana seized in Vientiane Province were destroyed on 12 May by provincial narcotics control and suppression authorities in the presence of several officials from other services concerned in the province. The destroyed marijuana was discovered and seized by provincial economic police authorities in their search for marijuana plantations operated by certain opportunists in many localities in the province since mid-1993. The destroyed haul was valued at 12.8 million kip [Lao currency]. Fifty-three marijuana planters, mostly residents of Kasi District, were reprimanded and fined by the local authorities concerned in accordance with the law.
